Ghost in the Shell;;89;;97;;NC;;In this Japanese animation, cyborg federal agent Maj. Motoko Kusanagi (Mimi Woods) trails "The Puppet Master" (Abe Lasser), who illegally hacks into the computerized minds of cyborg-human hybrids. Her pursuit of a man who can modify the identity of strangers leaves Motoko pondering her own makeup and what life might be like if she had more human traits. With her partner (Richard George), she corners the hacker, but her curiosity about her identity sends the case in an unforeseen direction.;;Sci-fi,Anime,Action;;Mamoru Oshii;;1995;;Richard Epcar,Mimi Woods,William Frederick Knight,Tom Wyner,Christopher Joyce,Michael Sorich,Simon Prescott,Skip Stellrecht;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ghost_in_the_shell